		<h2>Rapidly Create & Analyze Piping Systems of Any Complexity with the Least Effort</h2>
		<p>CAEPIPE (kay-pipe), the 1<sup>st</sup> pipe stress analysis software on PC (1983), <em>continues to be the preferred piping stress analysis tool</em> for static and dynamic pipe stress analysis of systems of <em>any complexity</em> in any industry. </p>
        <p>With CAEPIPE's world-acclaimed productivity-enhancing 3D modeler, our piping stress analysis software, CAEPIPE lets you analyze for the effects of weight, 10 pressures and temperatures, earthquake, time varying and harmonic loads, among others, and <strong>interactively and iteratively design your system for optimum configuration in the shortest time</strong>.
</p>
		<p>CAEPIPE also checks for piping code and guideline compliance (ASME, B31, International codes, API, NEMA) and can export data to select major plant design systems (AVEVA and CADMATIC currently). We offer many <a href="data-translators.php">data translators</a> to import piping geometry and design data from many platforms.</p>
        <p><a href="/pricing.php" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Pricing Request', 'Entry Link', 'caepipe.php_sectionA']);"><strong>REQUEST PRICING</strong> (Several  Options Available)</a></p>       
